    public class IntegerMap
extends com.emitrom.lienzo.client.core.shape.Layer
    The Class IntegerMap represents a map object of Integer. This is a subclass class extended from com.emitrom.lienzo.client.core.shape.Layer. It is able to display any number of service element by calculating the individual widget size.
